actor

Class Activity

  • java.lang.Object
    • actor.Activity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    public class Activity
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable
    Each event consists of different activities. The Activity class holds information such as: type, state, name, description, start time, end time, required agents, required items, prerequisites activities, participating agents and items and more. Each Agent receives a schedule that consists of activities arranged according to start time and that do not overlap
